description:
This extension adds up to 4 additional tabs on Servers to show OS-level information:
Users, Services, Disks, and Cron. Automatically creates these 6 parameters
needed to store OS-specific data: os_cron, os_partition, os_disks_physical,
os_disks_logical, os_users, os_services.
label: OS Info Extension
name: os_info_ext
